tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_data (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(255),
  treatment_recommendation TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE patients (
  id INT,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE treatments (
  treatment_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
  treatment_description VARCHAR(200),
  cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE doctors (
  doctor_id INT,
  doctor_name VARCHAR(50),
  specialty VARCHAR(50),
  experience_years INT,
  hospital VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  patient_age INT,
  patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
  patient_diagnosis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Treatments (
  treatment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
  treatment_description TEXT,
  treatment_duration INT,
  treatment_cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Physicians (
  physician_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  physician_name VARCHAR(50),
  physician_specialty VARCHAR(50),
  physician_experience_years INT,
  physician_contact VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE Diagnoses (
  diagnosis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  diagnosis_name VARCHAR(50),
  diagnosis_category VARCHAR(50),
  diagnosis_description TEXT,
  diagnosis_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name VARCHAR(50),

)

CREATE TABLE MedicalTests (

)

CREATE TABLE Medications (
  medication_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
